Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.63,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,SAY WON 'T STOP LOVE YOU{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.87,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,どんな小さな幸せも{\fad(500,800)}
